<br>
Sol a human and the king of the neighboring land of Solaris.  He was known for ruling his kingdom with an iron fist.  His army was undefeated and merciless on the battle field.  Ailill and Sol eventually wed each other bringing together to of the major forces in the world of Endura.  Now the land of Solaris belonged to Ailill herself and her King was willing to do whatever she commanded.  Ailill now having the power of Solaris under her wanted to take complete control over Endura.  She wanted all power like her mother.  So the forces of Ahura set out to take over Endura.  Once again the Three Powers rose up to face this threat to Endura.  During the final war Sol Bardok was slain.  This brought great misery upon Ailill and she went into a deep depression.  During the years of her depression the land of Ahura went from rolling green hills to dark gray rock.  One day while walking the halls of Lothor Durame, she remember the gift that was given to her by her mother.  The Life Crest could bring her husband back to her and give him eternal life.  She remembers the name of the thief who stole her gift.  The name Jared Highwind.  <br>
